name: All Items
query:
select 
	i.item_code as 'Item Code:Link/Item:100',
	i.item_name as 'Item Name:Data:350',
	i.item_group as 'Item Group:Link/Item Group:150',
	i.brand as 'Brand:Data:150',
	i.stock_uom as 'UOM:Link/UOM:60',
	ipd.head as 'Head:Float:80',
	ipd.discharge as 'Discharge:Float:80'
from `tabItem` i, `tabItem Performance Details` ipd where ipd.parent = i.name;
